75
00:02:49,883 --> 00:02:52,004
This is something that we all understand is important.

76
00:02:52,524 --> 00:02:55,006
We usually express this as a diagram

77
00:02:55,026 --> 00:02:56,827
where we've got challenge on one and skill on the other.

78
00:02:57,308 --> 00:03:00,289
And if it's got very low skill, sorry,

79
00:03:00,350 --> 00:03:02,391
very high skill requirement but low challenge,

80
00:03:02,431 --> 00:03:04,172
then a game becomes quite boring.

81
00:03:04,772 --> 00:03:07,814
And if it's got a low skill but high challenge,

82
00:03:07,834 --> 00:03:09,075
then the game becomes too difficult.

83
00:03:09,115 --> 00:03:10,356
It makes players really anxious.

84
00:03:11,157 --> 00:03:13,379
So we decide really that we should try and keep people

85
00:03:13,419 --> 00:03:15,120
what's called the flow channel.

86
00:03:15,901 --> 00:03:17,583
